  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Trader arrested for illegally storing petrol",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kattankudi Police arrested a businessman who was illegally stockpiling petrol last evening (30) and recovered a quantity of petrol from him, said the Kattankudi Police Station Crime Prevention Officer.",
        "He was arrested from a Kattankudi Divisional Business Center during a raid carried out by the Crime Prevention Officer under the direction of the Batticaloa District Senior Superintendent of Police under the direction of the Kattankudi Police Station Officer-in-Charge.",
        "The arrested person will be produced in the Batticaloa Magistrate's Court and the police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
